						<summary>

						<p>Slab outside the Narasimhasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription may be assigned to the 16th century on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It records the confirmation by Nedunūri Akkappaṅgāru of the previous gift of an <hi rend="italic">agrahāra</hi> by <hi rend="italic">Savdarlu</hi> to and the endowment of a <hi rend="italic">Rāmānujakūṭam</hi> to Marikaṇṭi Āchārya.</p>						

						</summary>
